{"tid":887220,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"「測試」 兩星期唔飲咖啡／茶， 睇下身體有咩變化","createTime":"2018-11-02T17:01:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-03T05:15:35.000Z","uid":123335,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"5888ed341ee67b29cebd418f05aef08e2be896a9","tid":887220,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T17:01:30.000Z","msg":"<ins>背景： </ins><br />\n其實本身我體質對咖啡因好敏感 <br />\n我第一次飲咖啡，會心跳加速，手震，不安<br />\n但由於經常性訓得少，返工眼訓<br />\n就接觸飲茶去提神，初初飲烏龍，綠茶，紅茶<br />\n當越飲越冇用既時候，就要飲到咖啡先提到神 <br />\n而去到呢個Point , 我飲咖啡已經唔會心跳加速，唔會手震 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n亦都由初初既每日一杯咖啡，變成每日兩杯，仲要隨心見到咩茶都飲 <br />\n但問題係，我好易由下午到晚上超攰 .... <br />\n就算做運動，都係攰攰地 ， 有種已經俾咖啡因 burn out 既感覺 ... <br />\n所以有呢個戒掉咖啡因類飲品／食物既念頭 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n---------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n即刻開始    Cold Turkey <br />\nDay 1 <br />\n11月3 日 （星期六 ） <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6728431effb85e00a5419ba40cac84357ddb9aba","tid":887220,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T17:02:03.000Z","msg":"會每日報告身體狀況 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7e8a8c09f5039669ce033f717f054db2088b7d5","tid":887220,"uid":30578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T17:03:03.000Z","msg":"扯唔到旗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55bb89cea9134560a3f199323100a4800e7b4ee0","tid":887220,"uid":27415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T17:03:24.000Z","msg":"哇！！支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f32844148b2c5f0bb7d15e13703b598b7d1532f5","tid":887220,"uid":123335,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d7e8a8c09f5039669ce033f717f054db2088b7d5","tid":887220,"uid":30578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"