},{"pid":"38bb514d9c15950fd923d5bd371833cdcc13450a","tid":887220,"uid":123335,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"36931038237235c1d86ffca33c262fdb531972cf","tid":887220,"uid":162988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T17:15:18.000Z","msg":"呢篇文解答到你點解飲完咖啡有以上問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.healthline.com/nutrition/caffeine-side-effects#section8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.healthline.com%2Fnutrition%2Fcaffeine-side-effects%23section8&d=iHEvM3WJGHg6PeUwLvKyrW6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=23ab6052\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.healthline.com/nutrition/caffeine-side-effects#section8</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T17:32:21.000Z","msg":"其實好難捉摸到何謂 <strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">&quot;moderate dose &quot;</span></strong> <br />\n咖啡因類飲品<br />\n好易隨住 tolerant（耐受性） 越飲越多<br />\n<br />\n總之我唔理了 <br />\n試下呢兩星期一滴都唔飲再講 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52ae078d209729fde720df39a9cdafbe34f45fe9","tid":887220,"uid":19624,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T02:23:38.000Z","msg":"留名先"},{"pid":"7a879fde24c9b9be6c80a651f97c79ee2a9f79b0","tid":887220,"uid":141782,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T02:43:13.000Z","msg":"一日六七杯 已經完全冇任何效<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb4aec0dd320a2a18f2637fccf0f35068cd75c79","tid":887220,"uid":72197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T02:58:16.000Z","msg":"一様<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cae40bbf81b936227733ba07ff50400d5a364a04","tid":887220,"uid":26752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T04:31:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一様<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fca78121f0fecce6a2499595da1003768465cb4f","tid":887220,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T05:01:25.000Z","msg":"戒斷症候群"},{"pid":"6ad7e9efa719318d0fcd204ff4f80edba2cd7c62","tid":887220,"uid":36688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T05:04:12.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"8eec83be13087e944015b6135531a540c5888cc7","tid":887220,"uid":9125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T05:15:35.000Z","msg":"前嗰幾年一直唔點飲咖啡，今年由年頭開始飲返，一日一杯，有foam嘅，到上個月兩杯，重要第二杯係齋啡。<br />\n日日收工後都攰到仆街，年頭都冇咁嘅情況"}]}